d(m,n)=\left\vert\frac{1}{m}-\frac{1}{n}\right\vert,
m,n\in\mathbb{N}
d:XxX\rightarrow\mathbb{R}
M1)
d(x,y)=0\Leftrightarrow x=y
M2)
d(x,y)=d(y,x)
M3)
d(x,y)\leq d(x,z)+d(z,y),
x,y,z\in X
M1)
\vert a\vert=0\Leftrightarrow a=0, and \frac{a}{b}=\frac{c}{d}\Leftrightarrow ad=bc
d(m,n)=\left\vert\frac{1}{m}-\frac{1}{n}\right\vert=0\Leftrightarrow \frac{1}{m}-\frac{1}{n}=0\Leftrightarrow\frac{1}{m}=\frac{1}{n}\Leftrightarrow m=n,
M2)
d(m,n)=\left\vert\frac{1}{m}-\frac{1}{n}\right\vert \cdot 1=\left\vert\frac{1}{m}-\frac{1}{n}\right\vert \cdot \vert -1 \vert=\left\vert(-1)\left(\frac{1}{m}-\frac{1}{n}\right)\right\vert=\left\vert\frac{1}{n}-\frac{1}{m}\right\vert=d(n,m)
M3)
M3)
d_A
A
d(m, n) = \left|\frac{1}{m} - \frac{1}{n}\right|
A = \mathbb{N}
B = \mathbb{R}
f(n) = \frac{1}{n}
d_B
\mathbb{R}
d_B(x, y) = |x-y|
